overview: Get ready for a wild and dirty ride. At the Stud Ranch: Hung n' Strung, you'll take a walk on the wild side! Buckshot boys are clean boys doing dirty things. Hung and strung, the boys at Stud Ranch get downright filthy. A hard day's work at this ranch involves a roll in the hay, plenty of rope and a riding saddle. Oh you'll definitely be breaking a sweat - hog-tied and horny, these hard bodies get worked to the limit.
title: Stud Ranch: Hung N' Strung
